<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ subject }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1><span style="color:#a85f31ff">I</span><span style="color:#ecb737ff">M</span><span style="color:#d45842ff">P</span><span style="color:#47a8afff">R</span><span style="color:#98a239ff">O</span><span style="color:#3c66a6ff">T</span><span style="color:#7e4994ff">Ř</span><span style="color:#a44c7dff">E</span><span style="color:#768f89ff">S</span><span style="color:#7e8845ff">K</span></h1>
            <p>Festival improvizace</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            {{ body|raw }}
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Tento e-mail byl odeslán automaticky, neodpovídej na něj.<br>
            Pro dotazy nás kontaktuj na <a href="mailto:improtresk@improlab.art">improtresk@improlab.art</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
